Happy birthday to my momma!!! My aunts and uncles always tell me stories about you back in the day as if I was “you” and was there with y’all. But when they realize that I’m not you and I’ll tell them that I wasn’t there then they’ll tell me that I am you!!! They see “you” in me so much that it confuses them!! Real talk!! It’s creepy sometimes lol. Whatever she did she did it the Fly way!! Fly.Cee is the name that she lived up to and I followed suit in every way formidable!!! Sometimes I think about her being taken away from me and I’ll get angry but it’ll soon get washed away when I think about how many blessings she left me with! My family, character and talent!! Hug y’all mother if you still have one because you only get ONE! That’s one of the 2 family members you can only get one of. We love you down here and continue to get your rest!! ❤️❤️❤️ #HappyBirthdayFlyCee

Our coach couldn’t adjust to losing Chubb and our QB play and special teams struggled and so did the O-Line. I still love my dawgs and and I’m praying for @nchubb27 🙏🏾 #MondayNightFootball #ClevelandBrowns #Nfl #nflseason  #GoBrowns ❤️

My son and I recorded a potty training song together and I decided to make a cartoon for it since he loves Gracie’s corner so much! He hasn’t seen it yet but I’ll be sure to record his reaction to it when he does! There’s a cartoon called Tooty Ta that’s not for kids but it’s set up like it’s for kids but I did my research and found out that the word Tooty Ta isn’t a word for kids. So monitor what your kids watch on YouTube because there’s a lot of perverse people making songs to mislead children! If you like our song then feel free to share, post and comment because we appreciate the support! Thank you for watching 🙏🏾🙏🏾 

P.S. having a kid changed my perspective on a lot of things. For the best!
